keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
# Add an additional mapping for Escape:
mapkey <c-c> <c-[>
map o Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
unmap h
unmap l
unmap f
map h previousTab
map l nextTab
map f LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
# Disable <c-[>:
mapkey <c-[> <anyOldJunk>
